    "content": "<p>Lead Full‑Stack Engineer focused on decentralized web applications (dApps), with 10+ years building and scaling Node.js/TypeScript systems in production.&nbsp;Recently led the launch of Tanssi, Moonbeam, and DataHaven dApps, owning architecture and hands‑on implementation across frontend, backend, AWS infrastructure, and testing.</p>"
