        {
          "id": "f6f1xt2rpi5045buwoe5kcoq",
          "hidden": false,
          "company": "OpsLayer, Inc.",
          "position": "Lead Software Engineer",
          "location": "Remote",
          "period": "January 2025 - now",
          "website": {
            "url": "https://opslayer.com",
            "label": ""
          },
          "description": "<ul><li><p>Led team of 7 engineers on Tanssi, DataHaven, and Glacis dApps, handling hiring (grew 3→7), task assignment, and mainnet launches from scratch.</p></li><li><p>Drove all technical decisions for the new DataHaven dApp, defining frontend architecture and integrations with Main Storage Provider backend services + DataHaven chain.</p></li><li><p>Owned end-to-end Tanssi dApp delivery, coordinating Next.js/Mantine frontend, backend, and AWS infrastructure.</p></li><li><p>Provided architecture guidance for Glacis projects (Scan App, Airlif API).</p></li></ul><p></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org\">TypeScript</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://react.dev\">React</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://nextjs.org\">Next.js</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://mantine.dev/\">Mantine</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://wagmi.sh/\">WAGMI</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://viem.sh/\">Viem</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://docs.ethers.org/v5/\">Ethers.js</a> •</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://polkadot.js.org/docs/\">PolkadotJS</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://playwright.dev\">Playwright</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/\">AWS</a></p>",
          "roles": []
        },
        {
          "id": "q365bykblyvuxsa303hbq47n",
          "hidden": false,
          "company": "OpsLayer, Inc.",
          "position": "Technical Lead",
          "location": "Remote",
          "period": "June 2023 - December 2024",
          "website": {
            "url": "https://opslayer.com",
            "label": ""
          },
          "description": "<ul><li><p>Owned technical strategy for the Tanssi and Moonbeam dApps, including the architecture for XCM‑SDK cross‑chain interactions.</p></li><li><p>Mentored a team of 3 engineers on WAGMI, PolkadotJS integrations, and E2E testing (Playwright). Reviewed critical PRs before release.</p></li><li><p>Led Moonbeam frontend migration from Create React App to Next.js + AWS Amplify, improving performance and deployments.</p></li><li><p>Replaced Bulma with Mantine across both dApps, unifying UI components and simplifying maintenance.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org\">TypeScript</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://react.dev\">React</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://nextjs.org\">Next.js</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://mantine.dev/\">Mantine</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://wagmi.sh/\">WAGMI</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://viem.sh/\">Viem</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://polkadot.js.org/docs/\">PolkadotJS</a> •</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://playwright.dev\">Playwright</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/\">AWS</a></p>",
          "roles": []
        },
        {
          "id": "lf3nrkaovzygekjwhlrnvn5q",
          "hidden": false,
          "company": "PureStake, Inc.",
          "position": "Web3 Software Engineer",
          "location": "Remote",
          "period": "January 2022 - June 2023",
          "website": {
            "url": "https://purestake.com",
            "label": ""
          },
          "description": "<ul><li><p>Built wallet connection and state management for v1 Moonbeam dApp using Ethers.js, handling multi-chain interactions across Moonbeam, Moonriver, and Moonbase Alpha.</p></li><li><p>Led frontend migration from Create React App to Next.js + AWS Amplify, improving build times, SEO, and deployment workflows.</p></li><li><p>Introduced Playwright E2E testing across Moonbeam dApp, catching regressions before releases and setting team testing standards.</p></li><li><p>Established core Web3 patterns (Ethers.js → WAGMI/PolkadotJS transition) continued in Moonbeam v2 development.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org\">TypeScript</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://react.dev\">React</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://nextjs.org\">Next.js</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://docs.ethers.org/v6/\">Ethers.js</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://polkadot.js.org/docs/\">PolkadotJS</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://playwright.dev\">Playwright</a> • <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/\">AWS</a></p>",
          "roles": []
        },
